### Example 2: Admin 네비게이션 메뉴 (Glassmorphism)

**패턴**:
```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import { page } from '$app/stores';
  import { UsersSolid, ChartBar, Cube, GlobeAlt, LockClosed, Star, Cog6Solid } from '$lib/components/icons';
  
  const navItems = [
    { path: '/admin/users', icon: UsersSolid, label: '사용자 관리' },
    { path: '/admin/monitoring', icon: ChartBar, label: '모니터링' },
    { path: '/admin/gateway', icon: GlobeAlt, label: 'Gateway 설정' },
    { path: '/admin/mcp', icon: Cube, label: 'MCP 서버' },
    { path: '/admin/guardrails', icon: LockClosed, label: 'Guardrails' },
    { path: '/admin/evaluations', icon: Star, label: '평가 리더보드' },
    { path: '/admin/settings', icon: Cog6Solid, label: '설정' }
  ];
</script>

<nav class="flex items-center gap-2 overflow-x-auto scrollbar-none px-4 py-3 bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-900/70 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-white/20 dark:border-gray-700/20">
  {#each navItems as item}
    <a
      href={item.path}
      class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-out whitespace-nowrap
      {$page.url.pathname === item.path
        ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/90 via-secondary/90 to-accent/90 dark:from-primary-light/80 dark:via-secondary-light/80 dark:to-accent-light/80 text-white backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 dark:shadow-primary-light/20 border border-white/20 dark:border-gray-700/20 transform scale-105'
        : 'bg-white/40 dark:bg-gray-800/40 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-white/60 dark:hover:bg-gray-800/60 border border-gray-200/30 dark:border-gray-700/30 hover:shadow-md hover:scale-105'}"
    >
      <svelte:component this={item.icon} className="size-4" />
      <span class="hidden sm:inline">{item.label}</span>
    </a>
  {/each}
</nav>
```

**핵심 포인트**:
- 아이콘 + 텍스트 조합 (모바일에서는 아이콘만)
- Active 상태: 그라데이션 + 그림자 + scale-105
- Inactive 상태: 투명 배경 + hover 효과
- `scrollbar-none`으로 스크롤바 숨김

